50|$|A marital <b>life</b> <b>estate</b> is, in {{the common}} law {{tradition}} of the United States and Great Britain, a <b>life</b> <b>estate</b> held by the spouse (husband or wife) or widowed spouse, {{for the duration of}} that spouse's life.|$|R
