50|$|Remainder: A {{remainder}} {{arises when}} a tenant with a fee simple grants someone a <b>life</b> <b>estate</b> or conditional fee simple, and specifies {{a third party}} to whom the land goes when the <b>life</b> <b>estate</b> ends or the condition occurs. The third party {{is said to have}} a remainder. The third party may have a legal right to limit the life tenant's use of the land.|$|R
